  "root_text": {
    "an10.212:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10.212 ",
    "an10.212:0.2": "21. Karajakāyavagga ",
    "an10.212:0.3": "Dutiyanirayasaggasutta ",
    "an10.212:1.1": "“Dasahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṁ nikkhitto evaṁ niraye. ",
    "an10.212:1.2": "Katamehi dasahi? ",
    "an10.212:1.3": "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pāṇātipātī hoti luddo lohitapāṇi hatapahate niviṭṭho adayāpanno sabbapāṇabhūtesu. ",
    "an10.212:2.1": "Adinnādāyī hoti … ",
    "an10.212:2.2": "kāmesumicchācārī hoti … ",
    "an10.212:2.3": "musāvādī hoti … ",
    "an10.212:2.4": "pisuṇavāco hoti … ",
    "an10.212:2.5": "pharusavāco hoti … ",
    "an10.212:2.6": "samphappalāpī hoti … ",
    "an10.212:2.7": "abhijjhālu hoti … ",
    "an10.212:2.8": "byāpannacitto hoti … ",
    "an10.212:2.9": "micchādiṭṭhiko hoti viparītadassano: ",
    "an10.212:2.10": "‘natthi dinnaṁ …pe… ",
    "an10.212:2.11": "sayaṁ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedentī’ti. ",
    "an10.212:2.12": "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, dasahi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṁ nikkhitto evaṁ niraye. ",
    "an10.212:3.1": "Dasahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṁ nikkhitto evaṁ sagge. ",
    "an10.212:3.2": "Katamehi dasahi? ",
    "an10.212:3.3": "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pāṇātipātaṁ pahāya pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti nihitadaṇḍo nihitasattho lajjī dayāpanno, sabbapāṇabhūtahitānukampī viharati. ",
    "an10.212:4.1": "Adinnādānaṁ pahāya adinnādānā paṭivirato hoti … ",
    "an10.212:4.2": "kāmesumicchācāraṁ pahāya kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato hoti … ",
    "an10.212:4.3": "musāvādaṁ pahāya musāvādā paṭivirato hoti … ",
    "an10.212:4.4": "pisuṇaṁ vācaṁ pahāya pisuṇāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti … ",
    "an10.212:4.5": "pharusaṁ vācaṁ pahāya pharusāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti … ",
    "an10.212:4.6": "samphappalāpaṁ pahāya samphappalāpā paṭivirato hoti … ",
    "an10.212:4.7": "anabhijjhālu hoti … ",
    "an10.212:4.8": "abyāpannacitto hoti … ",
    "an10.212:4.9": "sammādiṭṭhiko hoti aviparītadassano: ",
    "an10.212:4.10": "‘atthi dinnaṁ …pe… ye imañca lokaṁ parañca lokaṁ sayaṁ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedentī’ti. ",
    "an10.212:4.11": "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, dasahi dhammehi samannāgato yathābhataṁ nikkhitto evaṁ sagge”ti. ",
    "an10.212:4.12": "Dutiyaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "an10.212:0.1": "Numbered Discourses 10.212 ",
    "an10.212:0.2": "21. The Body Born of Deeds ",
    "an10.212:0.3": "Heaven and Hell (2nd) ",
    "an10.212:1.1": "“Someone with ten qualities is placed in hell as if delivered there. ",
    "an10.212:1.2": "What ten? ",
    "an10.212:1.3": "It’s when a certain person kills living creatures. They’re violent, bloody-handed, a hardened killer, merciless to living beings. ",
    "an10.212:2.1": "They steal. … ",
    "an10.212:2.2": "They commit sexual misconduct. … ",
    "an10.212:2.3": "They lie. … ",
    "an10.212:2.4": "They speak divisively. … ",
    "an10.212:2.5": "They speak harshly. … ",
    "an10.212:2.6": "They indulge in talking nonsense. … ",
    "an10.212:2.7": "They’re covetous. … ",
    "an10.212:2.8": "They have cruel intentions. … ",
    "an10.212:2.9": "They have wrong view. … ",
    "an10.212:2.10": "",
    "an10.212:2.11": "",
    "an10.212:2.12": "Someone with these ten qualities is placed in hell as if delivered there. ",
    "an10.212:3.1": "Someone with ten qualities is placed in heaven as if delivered there. ",
    "an10.212:3.2": "What ten? ",
    "an10.212:3.3": "It’s when a certain person gives up killing living creatures. They renounce the rod and the sword. They’re scrupulous and kind, living full of sympathy for all living beings. ",
    "an10.212:4.1": "They give up stealing. … ",
    "an10.212:4.2": "They give up sexual misconduct. … ",
    "an10.212:4.3": "They give up lying. … ",
    "an10.212:4.4": "They give up divisive speech. … ",
    "an10.212:4.5": "They give up harsh speech. … ",
    "an10.212:4.6": "They give up talking nonsense. … ",
    "an10.212:4.7": "They’re content. … ",
    "an10.212:4.8": "They’re kind hearted. … ",
    "an10.212:4.9": "They have right view. … ",
    "an10.212:4.10": "",
    "an10.212:4.11": "Someone with these ten qualities is placed in heaven as if delivered there.” "
  },
